CODY:

08:01.250 --> 08:03.125
Not usually, no!

08:10.625 --> 08:13.375
Aww. It wants to play.

08:13.417 --> 08:15.375
( whale bellows )

08:15.417 --> 08:17.250
CODY:

08:15.417 --> 08:17.250
I think he wants us

08:15.417 --> 08:17.250
