But I could be wrong.

08:26.375 --> 08:28.709
Ahem.

08:28.750 --> 08:31.750
High Tide, looks like

08:28.750 --> 08:31.750
an underwater trip.

08:31.792 --> 08:33.792
I can help you with that.

08:40.417 --> 08:43.083
( whale singing )

08:43.125 --> 08:46.500
(  majestic theme playing  )

08:50.417 --> 08:51.834
VERNE:

08:50.417 --> 08:51.834
Beautiful.

08:51.875 --> 08:54.667
The undersea world

08:51.875 --> 08:54.667
reveals herself to us.

08:54.709 --> 08:58.333
Yes, a book about such things

08:54.709 --> 08:58.333
must be written.

