HIGH TIDE:

08:58.375 --> 09:00.250
Detecting another ship.

09:00.291 --> 09:03.333
( whale singing )

09:03.375 --> 09:07.375
Dad, I think it's the  Nemo!

09:03.375 --> 09:07.375
Uh, what is this  Nemo?

09:07.417 --> 09:08.917
I'm guessing

09:07.417 --> 09:08.917
it's the reason

09:08.959 --> 09:10.959
you were sent

09:08.959 --> 09:10.959
to these coordinates.

